def handlerate(value):
    if (value=="NEW" or value== "-"):
        return np.nan
    else:
        value= str(value).split('/')
        value=value[0]
        return float(value)
    
df['rate']=df['rate'].apply(handlerate)

def handlecoma(value):
    value=str(value)
    if ',' in value :
        value=value.replace(',','')
        return float(value)
    else:
        return float(value)

df['Cost2plate']= df['Cost2plate'].apply(handlecoma)
